Terms of Service for NSFW Guard
Last Updated: 09.04.2025

1. Introduction NSFW Guard ("the Bot") is a free Discord bot designed to help manage content in Discord servers. It is designed to detect and moderate explicit or inappropriate content in the form of images, links, and embeds. By inviting and using NSFW Guard on your server, you agree to the following Terms of Service.

2. Services Provided NSFW Guard is designed to help Discord server administrators monitor and moderate content within their servers. The bot performs the following actions:

Detection of explicit or inappropriate content in images and links.

Logging of actions taken, such as deleting inappropriate content.

The ability to configure language preferences and logging channels.

3. Data Collection NSFW Guard does not store or retain any personal information or content that could be lost. The bot operates by analyzing content such as images or links in real-time and deleting inappropriate content if necessary. No data is saved permanently, and no personal data is retained by NSFW Guard.

4. Usage Rules By using NSFW Guard, you agree not to misuse the bot or engage in any activity that might harm other users or the functionality of the bot. The bot will automatically remove any explicit or inappropriate content detected, but the bot cannot be held responsible for any unintended deletions or actions.

5. No Liability NSFW Guard is provided as-is and is free to use. The bot's creator does not assume responsibility for any damages or losses that may occur due to the use or misuse of the bot. By using the bot, you understand and agree that you are using the bot at your own risk.

6. Modifications to Terms of Service These Terms of Service may be updated from time to time. The most current version of these terms will always be available to review. By continuing to use NSFW Guard, you agree to the updated terms.

7. Acceptance of Terms By inviting and using NSFW Guard in your Discord server, you confirm that you have read and accepted these Terms of Service. If you do not agree with any part of these terms, you must discontinue the use of the bot.

